* Create Functions\nfor Reusable Logic
** Types
***_ Scalar: returns single value
***_ Table-valued: returns result set
***_ Temporary: session-only
** Languages
***_ SQL functions
***_ Python functions (requires pro/serverless warehouse)
** Benefits
***_ Governed objects in Unity Catalog
***_ Shared across teams and workspaces
***_ Catalog tracks ownership & usage
** SQL scalar example
***_ RETURNS DOUBLE RETURN price * (1 - rate)
** Python example
***_ LANGUAGE PYTHON AS $$...$$
